text: Lic. Adolfo López Mateos International Airport or Toluca International Airport, is an airport in Toluca Municipality, Mexico. It opened in 1966. ==Airlines== These are the airlines that go to Guadalajara Airport: *Aeromar *Aeroméxico (hub) *Alaska Airlines *American Airlines *Copa Airlines *Delta Air Lines *Delta Connection *Interjet *Magnicharters *TAR *United Airlines *United Express *VivaAerobus *Volaris ==References== Category:Toluca Category:Airports in Mexico Category:Transport in Mexico (state) Category:1966 establishments in North America Category:1960s establishments in Mexico Category:Buildings and structures in Mexico (state)
title: Lic. Adolfo López Mateos International Airport
